---
title: Crunchy Garlic Chicken with Roasted Veggies
description: We love panko breadcrumbs. They're larger and more delicate than normal breadcrumbs so crisp up better when cooked. Today we're using them to bring some crunch to a garlicky chicken breast served with roasted veggies. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crunchy-garlic-chicken-6f87f3bb.jpg
